title: Green Halo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Filipino, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small cafe run by activists who are committed to serving organic, vegan-friendly fare. Also serves fish and chicken. Vegetarian versions of standard Filipino dishes are offered, as well as pasta and veggie burgers. Wait times are long.
streetAddress: Shop 11, Cubao Expo Commercial Center, Romulo Street, Araneta Center, Cubao, Quezon City
